A very good masjid,  Located opposite to karur bus stand.

It is Idgah jumma masjid.

Masjid situated in a complex consists of Sumathy sweets, kokkarako biriyani and mashallah restaurant.

All five times prayers done with religious customs.

Working muslim people around this offer prayers here.
